## Metric definitions

Definitions live in `.ai_context/knowledge/metrics.md` (create on first
metric). A number without a pinned definition is not a result.

## Definition of done

- Numbers are **reproducible**: fixed data window, pinned parameters/seed,
  and the exact command recorded next to the result.
- No lookahead / survivorship bias in the data path — state how you checked.
- Limitations and data-quality caveats stated alongside the findings.
- Findings dated into `.ai_context/journal/`; stable conclusions promoted
  to `knowledge/`.

## Project rules

<!-- Only deviations from global defaults. Keep short. -->

- _(none yet)_

## Memory & mechanisms

- `INDEX.md` + `state.md` auto-injected each session via `.claude/` hooks.
- Run `/wrap` at session end.

## Long-horizon tasks

- Multi-stage pipeline work (> ~30 min autonomous) goes through
  `/task <description>` — milestone verify commands are pipeline slices
  (one day / one symbol / one cohort) or output-schema checks.
- Work happens on a `task/<slug>` branch; every passed gate is a commit.
- `/task --auto` runs unattended; intent calls land in spec.md as
  `[ASSUMED: ...]` for later review.
